Uses of Interface
com.cyc.kb.Context

  • Packages that use Context 
    Package Description
    com.cyc.kb
    Provides basic interfaces for manipulating CycL-based java objects, both for the purpose of making assertions and for retrieving terms and values via simple queries.
    com.cyc.kb.client
    The implementation of various interfaces specified in com.cyc.kb, refer to that package for a more detailed discussion of using the API.
    com.cyc.kb.config
    This package contains useful configuration utilities of the KB API.
    com.cyc.kb.quant
    Provides quantifications, not fully supported in 1.0.0-Preview release, and subject to change.
    com.cyc.query
    Provides the core classes for constructing, specifying, and running Cyc queries.
